:

1. "*Govorim* da ću uspeti." (I'm saying that I will succeed.)
2. "Šta *govoriš*?" (What are you saying?)
3. "Svi *govore* da je to tačno." (Everyone is saying that it's true.)
4. "*Govorim* ti da to nije tačno." (I'm telling you that it's not true.)
5. "On *govori* da je ona prelepa." (He is saying that she is beautiful.)